POSTMAN

Simple demo of a location based game for Android.

Using osmdroid for Openstreetmap.org (osm) maps.

Build Post stations and deliver letters to earn money in this game.

Note: This game is not production ready, it's just a demo.

Reference:
My book "Spieleprogrammierung mit Android Studio", chapter 7
https://www.rheinwerk-verlag.de/spieleprogrammierung-mit-android-studio_3537/

Updated to fit latest osmdroid version


